Nairobi Stock Exchange to Introduce New Indexes, Works With London’s FTSE

-- B y   E r i c   O m b o k
-- 
2011-07-14T06:18:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-14/nairobi-stock-exchange-to-introduce-new-indexes-works-with-london-s-ftse.html
The  Nairobi Stock Exchange  plans to
introduce new indexes, Vice Chairman Job Kihumba said.  “We are working very closely with international
organizations, especially the FTSE,” Kihumba told reporters in
 Kenya ’s capital today, without providing further details.  To contact the reporter on this story:
